<PageTitle>RTP Transmitter</PageTitle>

<h1>RTP Transmitter - AES67 Audio Streamer</h1>

<p class="lead">
    This application receives AES67/RTP audio streams over UDP and delivers them to your browser
    for real-time playback using <strong>Howler.js</strong> with the Web Audio API.
</p>

<div class="card mb-3">
    <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">Architecture</h5>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>UDP Listener</strong> — Receives AES67 RTP packets (L16/L24 PCM at 48kHz)</li>
            <li><strong>PCM Converter</strong> — Decodes big-endian PCM payloads into Float32 samples</li>
            <li><strong>SignalR Hub</strong> — Streams audio chunks to connected browsers in real-time</li>
            <li><strong>HowlerStream Plugin</strong> — Extends Howler.js with a SoundBuffer for gapless chunk playback via Web Audio API</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>

<p>
    Navigate to <a href="sapdiscovery"><strong>SAP Discovery</strong></a> to start listening.
</p>
